  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.10">
<l>vaṉperuvā ṉakamuyya vamara ruyya</l>
<l>maṇṇuyya maṇṇulakiṉ maṉica ruyyat</l>
<l>tuṉpamiku tuyarakala vayarvoṉ ṟillāc</l>
<l>cukamvaḷara vakamakiḻun toṇṭar vāḻa</l>
<l>aṉpoṭuteṉ ṟicainōkkip paḷḷikoḷḷum</l>
<l>maṇiyaraṅkaṉ ṟirumuṟṟat taṭiyār taṅkaḷ</l>
<l>iṉpamiku peruṅkuḻuvu kaṇṭu yāṉum</l>
<l>icaintuṭaṉē yeṉṟukolō virukku nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day I too shall fit in  and stay with the big groups of servants who swell with joy</l>
<l>seeing [them] in the holy courtyard of Him of decorated Raṅgam,</l>
<l>who sleeps facing the southern direction with love</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the firm, great heavens are redeemed; so that the immortals are redeemed;</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the earth is redeemed; so that the humans of the earth are redeemed;</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the sorrow of exceeding affliction departs;</l>
<l rend="indent">so that happiness without any slackening grows;</l>
<l rend="indent">so that servants who rejoice at heart live?</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
